# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:9
translate french jamiestudy0_7d7e4c95:

    # "I knock on the door and a few seconds later Jamie rushes to the door and answers."
    "Je frappe à la porte et quelques secondes plus tard, Jamie se précipite pour ouvrir."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:13
translate french jamiestudy0_5bae9e51:

    # gnd "Hey, [pcname]. What's up?"
    gnd "Salut, [pcname]. Quoi de neuf ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:14
translate french jamiestudy0_49bf17fe:

    # pc "Not much, just thought I'd see what you're up to and if you wanted to hang out."
    pc "Pas grand-chose, je voulais juste voir ce que tu faisais et si tu voulais traîner un peu."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:15
translate french jamiestudy0_21baa282:

    # gnd "Oh, well I was about to start studying for a test."
    gnd "Oh, eh bien j'étais sur le point de commencer à réviser pour un contrôle."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:16
translate french jamiestudy0_6cc3a5ff:

    # pc "Ah, well I'll leave you alone then. I should probably get some studying in too."
    pc "Ah, bon, je te laisse tranquille alors. Je devrais probablement réviser moi aussi."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:17
translate french jamiestudy0_15ee3cd5:

    # gnd "Want to join me? We could study together."
    gnd "Tu veux te joindre à moi ? On pourrait réviser ensemble."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:22
translate french jamiestudy0_d41d8cd9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_002.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_002.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:23
translate french jamiestudy0_e5466e94:

    # gnd "Great!"
    gnd "Super !"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:25
translate french jamiestudy0_b1fa7b3c:

    # gnd "Come on now, don't be pervy. Do you want to study or not?"
    gnd "Allez, ne fais pas le pervers. Tu veux réviser ou pas ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:30
translate french jamiestudy0_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice "voices/jamie_002.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_002.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:31
translate french jamiestudy0_e5466e94_1:

    # gnd "Great!"
    gnd "Super !"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:34
translate french jamiestudy0_77d566bd:

    # gnd "Okay then. Well I'll see you later then."
    gnd "D'accord alors. Bon, à plus tard."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:35
translate french jamiestudy0_209b1712:

    # pc "See ya."
    pc "À plus."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:36
translate french jamiestudy0_1557defd:

    # "With that, she goes back inside and I walk back over to my house."
    "Sur ce, elle rentre chez elle et je retourne chez moi."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:41
translate french jamiestudy0_77d566bd_1:

    # gnd "Okay then. Well I'll see you later then."
    gnd "D'accord. Bon, à plus tard alors."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:42
translate french jamiestudy0_209b1712_1:

    # pc "See ya."
    pc "À plus."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:43
translate french jamiestudy0_1557defd_1:

    # "With that, she goes back inside and I walk back over to my house."
    "Sur ce, elle rentre chez elle et je retourne chez moi."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:49
translate french jamiestudy0_a0d94bd3:

    # pc "I'll just grab my laptop real quick."
    pc "Je vais juste chercher mon ordi portable rapidement."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:50
translate french jamiestudy0_0d7dfb6d:

    # gnd "Alrighty."
    gnd "D'accord."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:53
translate french jamiestudy0_d47d13e8:

    # "I rush home and run up the stairs, grabbing my laptop from the desk in my bedroom, then run back down and over to Jamie's house again."
    "Je me précipite chez moi et monte les escaliers en courant, j'attrape mon ordi portable sur le bureau de ma chambre, puis je redescends en courant et retourne chez Jamie."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:56
translate french jamiestudy0_17909979:

    # "She is waiting right by the door for me."
    "Elle m'attend juste à côté de la porte."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:57
translate french jamiestudy0_e90b21a6:

    # gnd "Let's go up to my bedroom."
    gnd "Montons dans ma chambre."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:58
translate french jamiestudy0_050f909c:

    # pc "Sounds good."
    pc "Bonne idée."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:61
translate french jamiestudy0_2d11a3f1:

    # "I follow her up the stairs to her bedroom and we both sit on the bed."
    "Je la suis dans les escaliers jusqu’à sa chambre et on s’assoit tous les deux sur le lit."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:62
translate french jamiestudy0_cecfb5d5:

    # "She pulls out some books that she had to read while I open up the essay that I have been working on."
    "Elle sort quelques livres qu’elle doit lire pendant que j’ouvre la dissertation sur laquelle je travaille."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:63
translate french jamiestudy0_43cd5788:

    # "We don't talk a whole lot, but occasionally I see her looking up at me smiling."
    "On ne parle pas beaucoup, mais de temps en temps, je la vois lever les yeux vers moi en souriant."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:65
translate french jamiestudy0_0507e3ef:

    # "Which subject should I study?"
    "Quelle matière je devrais étudier ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:71
translate french jamiestudy0_562e0a86:

    # "I try to focus on my work, but it is difficult with her lying there like that."
    "J'essaie de me concentrer sur mon travail, mais c'est difficile avec elle allongée là comme ça."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:72
translate french jamiestudy0_6306f9ee:

    # "Part of me just wants to toss my laptop aside and roll over on top of her."
    "Une partie de moi a juste envie de balancer mon ordinateur portable et de me jeter sur elle."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:73
translate french jamiestudy0_30a96a1d:

    # "I wonder what she would do. Would she say no? Would she be into it?"
    "Je me demande ce qu'elle ferait. Est-ce qu'elle dirait non ? Est-ce que ça lui plairait ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:74
translate french jamiestudy0_6ab7d82e:

    # "I decide not to push my luck for now. Not until she gives me a clear signal."
    "Je décide de ne pas tenter le diable pour l'instant. Pas avant qu'elle ne m'envoie un signal clair."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:75
translate french jamiestudy0_388afa61:

    # "Our relationship is still a little rocky after the way I had treated her when we were younger."
    "Notre relation est encore un peu fragile après la façon dont je l'ai traitée quand on était plus jeunes."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:76
translate french jamiestudy0_b3f8928f:

    # "I like the way that things are going and I don't want to ruin them."
    "J'aime la façon dont les choses se passent et je ne veux pas tout gâcher."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:77
translate french jamiestudy0_08d0a0f6:

    # "She will make it clear to me when she is ready."
    "Elle me le fera savoir clairement quand elle sera prête."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:78
translate french jamiestudy0_cd9b1b6c:

    # "After a couple of hours of working on the essay, I feels like it is pretty much done."
    "Après quelques heures passées à travailler sur la dissertation, j'ai l'impression qu'elle est pratiquement terminée."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:79
translate french jamiestudy0_f7da6361:

    # "Which is good, because right then I hear the door downstairs open."
    "Ce qui tombe bien, car à ce moment-là, j'entends la porte du rez-de-chaussée s'ouvrir."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:83
translate french jamiestudy0_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice "voices/jamie_052a.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_052a.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:84
translate french jamiestudy0_694762e8:

    # gnd "Oh shit, what time is it?"
    gnd "Oh merde, quelle heure est-il ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:86
translate french jamiestudy0_d41d8cd9_3:

    # voice "voices/jamie_052b.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_052b.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:87
translate french jamiestudy0_90448217:

    # gnd "I didn't realize that it was so late. Daddy will kill you if he finds you in my bedroom."
    gnd "Je n'avais pas réalisé qu'il était si tard. Papa va te tuer s'il te trouve dans ma chambre."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:88
translate french jamiestudy0_4bba0230:

    # pc "Should I hide?"
    pc "Je devrais me cacher ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:90
translate french jamiestudy0_02419fb6:

    # gnd "I'll distract him and get him into the back yard. When we're back there, you sneak out the front."
    gnd "Je vais le distraire et l'attirer dans le jardin. Quand on sera là-bas, tu te faufileras par devant."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:91
translate french jamiestudy0_238bde54:

    # pc "Got it."
    pc "D'accord."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:92
translate french jamiestudy0_0784ddae:

    # gnd "I had a good time studying with you tonight, by the way."
    gnd "Au fait, j'ai passé un bon moment à réviser avec toi ce soir."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:93
translate french jamiestudy0_b7756d1b:

    # gnd "We should do it again sometime."
    gnd "On devrait recommencer un de ces jours."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:94
translate french jamiestudy0_2951ed74:

    # pc "Definitely."
    pc "Absolument."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:96
translate french jamiestudy0_fd213b46:

    # gnd "Okay, stay here until you hear us go out into the back yard."
    gnd "Bon, reste ici jusqu'à ce que tu nous entendes sortir dans le jardin."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:97
translate french jamiestudy0_63023601:

    # pc "Okay."
    pc "D'accord."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:100
translate french jamiestudy0_18efe5b1:

    # "With that, she walks out of the bedroom and down the stairs. I tuck my laptop under my arm and wait."
    "Sur ces mots, elle sort de la chambre et descend les escaliers. Je glisse mon ordinateur portable sous mon bras et j’attends."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:101
translate french jamiestudy0_23a9e57a:

    # "After a few moments, I hear the back door open and shut and I take the opportunity to sneak out and down the stairs."
    "Au bout de quelques instants, j’entends la porte arrière s’ouvrir et se refermer, et j’en profite pour me faufiler dehors et descendre les escaliers."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:104
translate french jamiestudy0_d7055002:

    # "I can hear them talking in the back of the house as I sneak out the front door and creep back over to my house."
    "Je les entends parler à l’arrière de la maison tandis que je me glisse par la porte d’entrée et que je retourne discrètement chez moi."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:106
translate french jamiestudy0_0859cfec:

    # "That was close. I mean, he wouldn't have really killed me though, right?"
    "On l’a échappé belle. Je veux dire, il ne m’aurait pas vraiment tué, quand même, n’est-ce pas ?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:107
translate french jamiestudy0_9979a58c:

    # "Right?"
    "N'est-ce pas ?"

